actions.text: Submitted in the Senate, considered, and agreed to without amendment by Voice Vote.
Called up by House by Unanimous Consent.
Resolution Agreed to in House by Voice Vote.
Message on Senate action sent to the House.

official_title: A concurrent resolution requesting the President to return the enrolled bill (S. 854) entitled "Nevada-Florida Land Exchange Authorization Act of 1988".

summary.text: Requests the President to return the enrolled bill S. 854 (Nevada-Florida Land Exchange Authorization Act of 1988) for its reenrollment with technical corrections.
